My overall evaluation of Mc Donald's restaurant is always poor.In my evaluation,I will use several criteria:
-The percentage of fat that they burgers might containt;
-The quantity of they burgers;
-The quality of the oil used to fry and;
-The daily percentage of calories served on every meal.

The most evidences that were persuasive to me are:-the gaining weight;
-the biological parameters changes (values of cholesterol,trans fat, liver enzymes);
-His heart feeling and;
-Hyposexual activities that his mentionned.

During Mann's lifetime, many major changes was occurring in American Society:
- Immigrant were entering into the Northeastern;
- Farmers were leaving rural areas to work in factories;
- Cities were growing rapidly with crime and poverty rise.
